Hidden Markov mark-recapture model to implement the survival analysis

Folder /code contains code to format data and run the model.

Folder /data contains tag meta-data and satellite tag track data. Acoustic tag detection data needed to run the model can be downloaded from:
https://purl.stanford.edu/kr436rw2508 (blocklab_pnas_geodata_wgsl_detects_2025mar21.csv).
